Privacy Policy



Tantransha, hereinafter referred to as "the Company," is committed to protecting the privacy and security of its users. This Privacy Policy outlines how the Company collects, uses, and protects information collected from users of the "Smart NFC" app (hereinafter referred to as "the App"). By using the App, you agree to the terms and conditions of this Privacy Policy.

Information Collection and Use

The App ( SmartNFC) does not collect or share any personal data on its servers. The Company does not collect any personally identifiable information (PII) from users of the App. Any data that is accessed or processed by the App is stored locally on the user's device and is not transmitted or shared with the Company or any third-party services.

The App may use NFC (Near Field Communication) technology to read or write data from NFC-enabled devices, such as NFC tags or cards. However, the data read or written by the App is stored locally on the user's device and is not transmitted or shared with the Company or any third-party services.

Information Security

The Company takes reasonable measures to protect the security and confidentiality of information collected by the App. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure and the Company cannot guarantee the absolute security of any information collected or transmitted through the App.

Children's Privacy

The App is not intended for children under the age of 13. The Company does not knowingly collect or solicit any personal information from children under the age of 13. If you believe that a child has provided personal information to the Company through the App, please contact us immediately at [CONTACT EMAIL], and we will take steps to delete such information from our records.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

The Company reserves the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time without prior notice. Any changes to the Privacy Policy will be effective immediately upon posting on the App. Your continued use of the App after any changes to the Privacy Policy constitutes your acceptance of such changes.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [CONTACT EMAIL].

Conclusion

The Company respects the privacy and security of its users and is committed to maintaining the confidentiality and integrity of any information collected or processed through the App. The App does not collect or share any personal data on its servers, and any data accessed or processed by the App is stored locally on the user's device. By using the App, you acknowledge and agree to the terms and conditions of this Privacy Policy.






